Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.09,0:00:03.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.30,0:00:07.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we somehow managed to \Nstop the Dragon Chain Cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.09,0:00:10.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We managed somehow once \NI rushed onto the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:12.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you trying to prove?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.39,0:00:14.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you're heavy, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:17.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I could see you being like, 0.05 tons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:19.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't measure it in tons!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:56.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.16,0:01:57.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:03.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And why did you crash land when \Nyou were only carrying one person?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:04.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause you're heavy, Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:07.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You just {\i1}have{\i0} to keep \Npushin' that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:08.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:11.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With the other Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:17.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:18.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:30.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Who Are Alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:35.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They just keep comin' out of the woodwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:37.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:39.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:45.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:53.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they aiming at Happy and Carla?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:57.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've turned most of the Exceeds \Nthat ran for it into lacrima!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:03:00.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left are those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:03.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now stand still, so we can turn you \Ninto our kingdom's magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:11.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't give a damn what happens to the \NExceed, if it's for your own magic power?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:16.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what the humans \Nare like on this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:22.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna let you hurt my \Nfriends, you filthy bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:25.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Save the Exceed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I met Gajeel on my way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Things have moved pretty far along.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel? You mean the informant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:37.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that his info \Nis always reliable, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:44.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kingdom is trying to sacrifice \Nthe Exceed, Earthland, and us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:47.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and make the entire world \Ntheirs to do as they please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let them get away with that, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:55.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Royal Army has a huge \Namount of magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:57.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could we win if we fought them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:02.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, the Royal Army has \Na number of very powerful foes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:07.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we even have a chance \Nof winning against them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:15.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Wheel, Trinity Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:17.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gravity Core!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:26.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Crimson!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Venus Photon Slicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:42.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Runesave!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:45.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She cut through the magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:47.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Silfarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:55.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:01.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:10.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I propose that we wait until the battle \Nbetween the Exceed and the Kingdom is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:14.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll both be tired \Nout, and when we show up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we could take them both out! How about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:19.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that method might have merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:22.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, make the \Nmost of the opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:26.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or, we could ally with the Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We put the Kingdom in our debt,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:32.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and get them to recognize us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:36.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This might be a chance \Nto make up with the Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:40.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Juvia-chan! You're so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:40.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:42.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate how you smother me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:46.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:52.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We should know better than anyone \Nthat the Kingdom isn't so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:03.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Far from making up with them, I bet \Nwe'd be treated even worse than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:07.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Droy's suggestion is also not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:13.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Exceed are wiped out, the Kingdom \Nwill surely move on to their next ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:18.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll suppress anyone who opposes them, \Nand we'll fall into a new dark age!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:21.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lose the one opening we have!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:25.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for humans to \Nbe fighting with the Exceed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:42.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no chance of winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:46.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's suffering from \Nlack of magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:51.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but their king sure has \Nplenty all for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:57.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for a \Nking to tax his people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:07:02.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Droma Anim is constantly absorbing \Nmagic power from the entire world...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:05.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ultimate magical weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:09.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's also the reason \Nit is a forbidden weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:13.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Once activated, I have a duty to \Nwin, for the sake of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:15.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:17.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just stealin' magic for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:19.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that with a straight face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:26.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See, we joined a guild so that we could live.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:30.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I might not know much 'bout this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:35.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But for the sake of all the living things \Nof this world, I will defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:39.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm scared, I really am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:42.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we shouldn't do \Nanything and just hide...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:47.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly speaking, as long as I can live \Ntogether in peace with Bis Bis, I'll be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:51.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... We shouldn't be searching \Nout danger ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:54.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bunch of spineless wimps!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:58.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Exceeds are all gone, \Nthey'll come after us next!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:02.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knows that, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:07.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter what you say, everyone \Nknows how fearsome the Kingdom is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:12.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, Fairy Tail here doesn't \Nhave any magic power left...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:15.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can only long-distance transfer once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:19.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we jump into this fight, \Nthere's no pulling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:25.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Lion, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:26.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:31.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:36.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:41.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Bullets?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:48.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:50.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:53.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:57.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, I hit an Exceed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:09:00.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! That's going to be our magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:05.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla, hang in there! Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:15.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, take Carla someplace safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:16.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Loke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:24.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:37.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think everyone's said their \Nopinion. It's about time to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:46.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want people to hear one last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:53.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now the Fairy Tail from Earthland is \Nfighting the Kingdom, risking their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:10:00.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Earthland's Natsu, Gray, \Nmyself, and everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:19.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate... everyone is going to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:27.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet! I can't be defeated here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:29.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just stand back and \Nwatch while they're killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:33.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to cut open a path to \Nour world's future ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:38.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu and Erza should still be fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:41.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't give up before they do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:46.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the only ones who can \Nstand against the Kingdom now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:48.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can do it! We can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:52.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:55.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Fairy Tail wizards!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:59.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use... We're just too outnumbered...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:22.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone... save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:35.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:38.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a tree that's moving on its own...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:39.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:50.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... Those guys who only ever run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:04.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll show you the power \Nof the bonds of friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:14.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Edolas Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:18.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout that. Were we late, Earth-Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:21.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Edo-Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:32.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:34.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pummel the Royal Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:36.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:40.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! The Earthland Fairy Tail is fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:42.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so we'll fight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stand, Earth-Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Double Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:51.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? And look at your clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:54.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Strip down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Put some clothes on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:57.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe there are two Grays!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:59.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia's in a pickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, I wish I were them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:04.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're me, so why can't you feel what I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:06.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at my beloved Juvia-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:09.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beloved Juvia-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:11.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia-chan, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:16.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't lose either, Al Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:17.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Bis Bis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:19.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...power of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:22.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeehaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:24.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's stronger than us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:28.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to show up Lucy, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:30.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:35.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you the strongest \Npower in Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:42.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:47.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's even faster than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:52.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray is drooling all over Juvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.75,0:13:55.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, Jet and Droy are \Ncontending for the strongest?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:57.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much completely backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:02.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Carla. Fairy Tail came to rescue us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:09.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our feelings are making this world change.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:13.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Lisanna-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:16.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're Shadow Gear, the strongest of them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Al Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:19.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Bis Bis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:23.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where you go, our \Nguild's making trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:34.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scarlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Knightwalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:46.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still even, after all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:48.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even? I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:53.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't experienced the \Nultimate form of the Ten Commandments!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:00.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Lance, Ravelt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:04.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A holy lance forged by the \Ngreatest blacksmith in Edolas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:08.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Its attack brings ultimate destruction \Nthat resounds out into the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Armadura Faerie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:23.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I need hardly explain why it \Nbears the name of our guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:26.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that's \Nyour strongest magic, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:29.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fascinating... Have at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My Ravelt...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:52.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:59.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With that attack, the floating \Nisland can no longer stay afloat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:02.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of us has any magic power left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:04.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet I will strike you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:11.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:19.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times you stand, \Nyou will never be able to defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:22.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those with magic power will rule the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:25.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something this world requires!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:29.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop twistin' logic to justify your actions!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:31.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You dolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:36.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know whether it requires it or not, \Nbut I do know I'm gonna bust that thing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:38.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Sky Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please refrain from \Nwasting all the magic power?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:52.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because all your magic power is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:55.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even joke about that! \NMy magic power is my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:57.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't no one else's but mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:01.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pillar of the Iron Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:15.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your magic power, your very lives... \NThey're all mine for the taking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:24.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:29.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia-chan, so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:34.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off me! Try taking a page out of \Nthat other Gray's book and strip down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:39.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards! Don't you realize \Nwhat you're doing is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:46.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They should realize.  There should be some \Npeople against what the Kingdom is doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:52.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If they disobey, they'll be killed, \Nso they have no choice but to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:55.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,War is just so tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:59.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I would much rather have a tea \Nparty with everyone, but no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:04.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, we have no choice \Nbut to counterattack them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:09.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Earth-Lucy... Is the \Nguy with glasses your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:11.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's not! He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:13.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we look that way to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:16.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're also Lucy, so I guess you can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate playboys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:21.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:25.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Edolas's Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Exceeds, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:31.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay... Shall I stay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:34.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, but I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:36.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy is here for me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:50.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be nearby, and if anything \Nhappens, I'll protect you. Rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:56.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Edolas's Wendy is also kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:57.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:03.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose, for the sake of eternal energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:08.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For your accursed "eternity", how many \Nsacrifices have been made in your "now"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:14.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oppress and steal! Coerce and steal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:16.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hate the other! Destroy the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:19.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what humans do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:23.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,People should love people more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:27.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They stand up for the people they care about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:30.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They pick up swords for those who shed tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:36.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you hear this world screaming \Nin agony, Knightwalker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:41.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The screams of the world? I'm sure \NI can feel them more than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:45.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic drying up... \NAnd because of that, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:48.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! When I say the world, \NI mean the living things!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:53.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is heading toward oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:57.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a world running out of \Nmagic, plunging toward its death!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:20:00.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A person from Earthland like \Nyou could never understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.21,0:20:03.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The anxiety, fear, despair \Nof having magic disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:07.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't survive unless we get \Nan eternal source of magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:11.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're alive, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:11.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:14.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any magic \Npower, but we're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:20.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at us! We've both used it all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:23.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, we aren't dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:27.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have the strength to overcome \Nthe weakness and the fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:30.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:36.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear this, Erza! Inside of you is the same \Nfrailty and evil that lies within me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:40.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I know you hold a \Nheart that can love others!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:43.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to the voices of the \Nliving, with your entire heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:48.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:50.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak with your true voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:55.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:20:58.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:01.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:05.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:07.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something fell down, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:09.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:21.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any strength left to move...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:23.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:28.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't match you... You win, Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:34.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This battle is not one that could \Nbe won or lost. We're both Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:38.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:44.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The chamber that creates the Anima?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:53.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince, what in the world are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.88,0:21:56.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I observed Earthland for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:22:00.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There was strife, but it \Nwas a wonderful world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:04.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure they'll accept this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:07.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince! You can't mean... That's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.96,0:22:09.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is far too radical!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:13.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only way to \Nrid this world of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:17.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will create a world where people \Ncan be open with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.70,0:22:20.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will throw the Anima into reverse...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:24.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...and rid this world of all its magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:59.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... It's just a fake \Ndragon but it's pretty tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.93,0:24:02.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they don't call it an \Nultimate weapon for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.86,0:24:06.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... It's a real pain that \Nmagic doesn't work on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.02,0:24:09.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have three Dragon Slayers on our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.27,0:24:10.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way we'd lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.83,0:24:13.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's go another round!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.02,0:24:16.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: I'm Standing Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.04,0:24:19.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Natsu, do you have any magic power left?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.39,0:24:21.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I didn't, I'd do it somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.58,0:24:24.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the stubborn \Npride of Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:26.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
